{
  "text": "Patients ineligible for ASCT are treated with supportive therapy and non-intensive chemotherapy, like hypomethylating agents (Table 2) , because the benefit of intensive therapy is now limited only to patients who can undergo a transplant. MPN-BP (n = 10) ongoing NR [CITATION_1] Abbreviations: HMAs, hypomethylating agents; ORR, overall response rate.",
